ricev7_all_famInfo = pd.read_csv("./csv/all.pfam",sep='\t')
print(ricev7_all_famInfo.columns)
ricev7_all_famInfo_gene_and_gene_family = ricev7_all_famInfo.reindex(columns=['model','hmm_acc'])
ricev7_all_famInfo_gene_and_gene_family = ricev7_all_famInfo_gene_and_gene_family.loc[ricev7_all_famInfo.model.str.contains('LOC_')]
ricev7_all_famInfo_gene_and_gene_family.columns = ['gene', 'gene_family']
for i in range(len(ricev7_all_famInfo_gene_and_gene_family)):
    gene_ = ricev7_all_famInfo_gene_and_gene_family.iloc[i]['gene']
    gene_family_ = ricev7_all_famInfo_gene_and_gene_family.iloc[i]['gene_family']
    gene_modify = ''
    gene_family_modify = ''
    for j in range(len(gene_)):
        if gene_[j] == '.':
            break
        else:
            gene_modify = gene_modify + gene_[j]
    for j in range(len(gene_family_)):
        if gene_family_[j] == '.':
            break
        else:
            gene_family_modify = gene_family_modify + gene_family_[j]
    ricev7_all_famInfo_gene_and_gene_family.iloc[i]['gene'] = gene_modify
    ricev7_all_famInfo_gene_and_gene_family.iloc[i]['gene_family'] = gene_family_modify
    print('%d'%(i),end='\r')

ricev7_gene_family_list = list(ricev7_all_famInfo_gene_and_gene_family.gene_family.unique())

def extract_gtf2bed(gff_gene_table, out_bed_file, target_list):
    out_file = open(out_bed_file,'w')
    #print(gtf_list['explanation'].head())
    for index in range(len(target_list)):#index为搜索当前基因
        sub_gff = gff_gene_table.loc[gff_gene_table.explanation.str.contains(target_list[index])]
        #range_list = []
        #搜索range min max
        '''
        for i in range(len(sub_gtf)):
            range_list.append(sub_gtf.iloc[i]['start'])
            range_list.append(sub_gtf.iloc[i]['end'])
        '''
        #print(range_list, min(range_list), max(range_list) )
        gene_family_ = list((ricev7_all_famInfo_gene_and_gene_family.loc[ricev7_all_famInfo_gene_and_gene_family.gene.str.contains(target_list[index])])['gene_family'])
        #if len(sub_gff['chrom'].unique()) == 1 and len(gene_family_) == 1:
        if len(sub_gff['chrom'].unique()) == 1:
            out_file.write("%s\t%d\t%d\t%s\t%s\t%s\n"%(sub_gff['chrom'].unique()[0], min(sub_gff.start), max(sub_gff.end), target_list[index], gene_family_[-1], ricev7_gene_family_list.index(gene_family_[-1])))
            print("Accomplished of index %d of %s, %s [%d %d] %d" % (index, target_list[index], sub_gff['chrom'].unique()[0], min(sub_gff.start), max(sub_gff.end), max(sub_gff.end)-min(sub_gff.start)), end='\r')
        else:
            print("%s ERROR ! "%(target_list[index]), end='\n')

sequences_label = []
for i in range(len(sequence_divition)):#找每条序列内部的基因，并获取其所在家族的label向量
    chr_ = sequence_divition.iloc[i]['chrom']
    start_ = sequence_divition.iloc[i]['start']
    end_ = sequence_divition.iloc[i]['end']
    sub_related_gene_family = gene_and_gene_family_label.loc[gene_and_gene_family_label.chrom.str.contains(chr_)]
    print("[%d] %s %s %s, %s"%(i, chr_, start_, end_, len(sub_related_gene_family) ),end='\r')
    label_ = []
    for j in range(len(sub_related_gene_family)):
        #该if条件要画图理解
        if sub_related_gene_family.iloc[j]['start'] < end_ and sub_related_gene_family.iloc[j]['end'] > start_ :
            label_.append(sub_related_gene_family.iloc[j]['gene_family_label'])
    sequences_label.append(label_)

#the input a and b should all be list
def jaccard_sim(a, b):
    unions = len(set(a) & (set(b)))
    intersections = len(set(a) | (set(b)))
    #print(unions, intersections)
    if intersections == 0:
        return 0
    else:
        return 1. * unions / intersections

jaccard_sim_result = np.zeros((len(sorted_sequences_label),len(sorted_sequences_label)),dtype='float32')

for x in range(len(sorted_sequences_label)):
    for y in range(len(sorted_sequences_label)):
        jaccard_sim_result[x, y] = jaccard_sim(sorted_sequences_label[x],sorted_sequences_label[y])

def p681_evaluate(mh_table, nip_table, save_pic):
    scale_x = 4
    scale_y = int(len(sample_name)/scale_x)
    fig, axs = plt.subplots(scale_x, scale_y, figsize=(20,15))
    basenji_precision = []
    for sample in sample_name:
        selected_ = []
        i = sample_name.index(sample)
        while i < len(basenji_pca_model_mh):
            selected_.append(mh_table.iloc[i]['ref_lpred'] - nip_table.iloc[i]['ref_lpred'])
            i=i+len(sample_name)

        from kern_smooth import densCols
        from matplotlib.colors import ListedColormap
        densities = densCols(selected_, comparison_data_map2NIP.nm_alt_ref, nbin=50)
        index = sample_name.index(sample)
        axs[int(index/scale_y),int(index%scale_y)].scatter(selected_, comparison_data_map2NIP.nm_alt_ref, 
                s=8,c=densities,alpha=1,cmap=ListedColormap(sns.color_palette("RdBu_r", 7).as_hex()),rasterized=True)
        #axs[int(index/scale_y),int(index%scale_y)].set_ylabel('nm_alt_ref')
        count = 0
        for i in range(len(comparison_data_map2NIP.nm_alt_ref)):
            if(selected_[i] * comparison_data_map2NIP.nm_alt_ref[i] > 0):
                count=count+1
        from scipy.stats import pearsonr
        r,_ = pearsonr(selected_, comparison_data_map2NIP.nm_alt_ref)
        print("%s : %0.3f , %0.3f"%(sample, count/float(len(comparison_data_map2NIP.nm_alt_ref)), r**2))
        axs[int(index/scale_y),int(index%scale_y)].set_title(r'%s : %0.3f' %(sample,count/float(len(comparison_data_map2NIP.nm_alt_ref))))
        axs[int(index/scale_y),int(index%scale_y)].axvline(x=0,c='grey',linestyle='--')
        axs[int(index/scale_y),int(index%scale_y)].axhline(y=0,c='grey',linestyle='--')
        basenji_precision.append(count/float(len(comparison_data_map2NIP.nm_alt_ref)))
    #plt.suptitle('basenji_precision')
    if save_pic is not None:
        plt.savefig(save_pic,dpi=600)
    
    model_precision = basenji_precision#改个变量名，防止误解
    return model_precision

比较三个模型的性能¶

synteny_training_result是使用 https://funricegenes.github.io/famInfo.table.txt 计算jaccard系数划分基因家族训练的结果；

pca_kmeans_cluster_synteny_result是使用 http://rice.plantbiology.msu.edu/pub/data/Eukaryotic_Projects/o_sativa/annotation_dbs/pseudomolecules/version_7.0/all.dir/all.pfam 得到2843条131kb的序列的binary家族向量，再PCA降维到30维，再将2843条序列的降维结果聚类成300个簇划分基因家族做训练的结果；

#name_list = ['synteny_training','pca_kmeans_cluster_synteny','synteny_random_reference']
name_list = ['r2','prc','auc','average','681_points_precision']
synteny_training = [
    synteny_training_result['r2'].mean(),
    synteny_training_result['prc'].mean(),
    synteny_training_result['auc'].mean(),
    (synteny_training_result['r2'].mean()+synteny_training_result['prc'].mean()+synteny_training_result['auc'].mean())/3,
    np.mean(synteny_training_precision)
]
pca_kmeans_cluster_synteny = [
    pca_kmeans_cluster_synteny_result['r2'].mean(),
    pca_kmeans_cluster_synteny_result['prc'].mean(),
    pca_kmeans_cluster_synteny_result['auc'].mean(),
    (pca_kmeans_cluster_synteny_result['r2'].mean()+pca_kmeans_cluster_synteny_result['prc'].mean()+pca_kmeans_cluster_synteny_result['auc'].mean())/3,
    np.mean(pca_model_precision)
]
random_reference = [
    synteny_random_reference_result['r2'].mean(),
    synteny_random_reference_result['prc'].mean(),
    synteny_random_reference_result['auc'].mean(),
    (synteny_random_reference_result['r2'].mean()+synteny_random_reference_result['prc'].mean()+synteny_random_reference_result['auc'].mean())/3,
    np.mean(random_reference_precision)
]
x = np.arange(len(name_list))
bar_width = 0.15

plt.figure(figsize=(16,8))
for a,b,c,d in zip(x, synteny_training, pca_kmeans_cluster_synteny, random_reference):
    plt.text(a,b,'%.3f' %b, ha='center',va='bottom')
    plt.text(a+bar_width,c,'%.3f' %c, ha='center',va='bottom')
    plt.text(a+bar_width*2,d,'%.3f' %d, ha='center',va='bottom')

# 有几个模型就写几句bar plot
plt.bar(x, synteny_training, bar_width, align="center", color="orange", label="synteny_training", alpha=0.5)
plt.bar(x+bar_width, pca_kmeans_cluster_synteny, bar_width, color="red", align="center", label="pca_kmeans_cluster_synteny", alpha=0.5)
plt.bar(x+bar_width*2, random_reference, bar_width, color="green", align="center", label="random_reference", alpha=0.5)

plt.xticks(x+bar_width*1.0, name_list)
#plt.xticks(rotation=6)

plt.xlabel("Indicator")
plt.ylabel("Performance")
plt.title('Performance_of_each_models')
plt.legend(loc='upper left')

plt.savefig("./pdf/performance_of_3models_bar_plot.pdf",dpi=600)
